hopobject.body: How do you do? venturemedicalassociates.com These products did not take off – for a bunch of reasons. People don't like forking over money to an insurance company with no guarantee of getting anything back. Secondly, while Americans are increasingly aware of longevity gains, their grasp of longevity risk is much weaker. And, of course, there was that nasty recession that turned everyone's attention to much more troubling present financial challenges.
